{
  "texts": [
    "By allocating attention weights to various input places, the self-attention mechanism enables interpretability.",
    "This makes it possible to visualize the significance and relevance of particular characteristics in the prediction process.",
    "The limitation of the proposed model is; It becomes difficult to understand the transformers architecture, particularly when it becomes deeper and complicated.",
    "Especially, to grasp how the model generates particular predictions or what sequence elements are essentials.",
    "To address this issue, we used attention visualization approaches, which gave us helpful insight about the framework's decision-making process."
  ]
}